original_query: SELECT u.Id, ph.UserId FROM postHistory as ph, posts as p, users as u, badges as b WHERE b.UserId = u.Id AND p.OwnerUserId = u.Id AND ph.UserId = u.Id AND p.AnswerCount>=0 AND p.FavoriteCount>=0 AND p.CreationDate<=CAST('2014-09-03 03:32:35' AS TIMESTAMP) AND u.CreationDate<=CAST('2014-09-12 22:21:49' AS TIMESTAMP)
rewritten_query: CREATE VIEW E3 AS SELECT users.id AS E3_id FROM users AS users WHERE users.creationdate <= TIMESTAMP '2014-09-12 22:21:49'
CREATE VIEW E1 AS SELECT posthistory.userid AS E1_userid FROM posthistory AS posthistory
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E3_stage1_0 AS SELECT * FROM E3 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E1 WHERE E3.E3_id=E1.E1_userid)
CREATE VIEW E4 AS SELECT badges.userid AS E4_userid FROM badges AS badges
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E3_stage1_1 AS SELECT * FROM E3_stage1_0 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E4 WHERE E3_stage1_0.E3_id=E4.E4_userid)
CREATE VIEW E2 AS SELECT posts.owneruserid AS E2_owneruserid FROM posts AS posts WHERE posts.answercount >= 0 AND posts.favoritecount >= 0 AND posts.creationdate <= TIMESTAMP '2014-09-03 03:32:35'
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E3_stage1_2 AS SELECT * FROM E3_stage1_1 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E2 WHERE E3_stage1_1.E3_id=E2.E2_owneruserid)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E1_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E1 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E3_stage1_2 WHERE E3_stage1_2.E3_id=E1.E1_userid)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E4_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E4 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E3_stage1_2 WHERE E3_stage1_2.E3_id=E4.E4_userid)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E2_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E2 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E3_stage1_2 WHERE E3_stage1_2.E3_id=E2.E2_owneruserid)

CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E_stage3 AS SELECT E3_stage1_2.E3_id AS E3_id, E1_stage2_0.E1_userid AS E1_userid FROM E3_stage1_2, E1_stage2_0, E4_stage2_0, E2_stage2_0 WHERE E3_stage1_2.E3_id=E1_stage2_0.E1_userid AND E3_stage1_2.E3_id=E4_stage2_0.E4_userid AND E3_stage1_2.E3_id=E2_stage2_0.E2_owneruserid
